      "content": "# expense-report model tracks expense claims and approvals\n\n`powerhouse/expense-report` (18 ops) handles expense claim workflows. Part of the Reporting zone alongside [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]] and [[snapshot-report model provides point-in-time data captures]].\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nReporting zone. May reference [[accounts model defines the chart of accounts structure]] for expense categorization and feed into [[account-transactions model tracks financial transaction records]] for financial recording.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
